{"tid":2445343,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"突襲封半山豪宅　政府人員備午餐肉予封區居民","createTime":"2021-03-13T14:21:45.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T18:17:02.000Z","uid":3747,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c8bec5cb2e2ae40a5e896db97bed338efc02a4d8","tid":2445343,"uid":3747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:21:45.000Z","msg":"【突襲封半山豪宅　政府人員備午餐肉予封區居民】<br />\n<br />\n政府今晚（13 日）再突襲封區，晚上約 8 時半封鎖西半山雍景臺、殷樺花園，以及附近的一段羅便臣道。政府指，由於附近近期出現確診個案，經評估後相關區域感染風險較高，故決定封區，目標是明早 9 時完成行動。<br />\n<br />\n政府人員於晚上約 9 時以貨車運送食物及物資到受限區域中。現場所見，貨車載有十數箱紙皮盒，盒內可見其中一款提供予封區居民的食物為長城牌午餐肉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3976973512388239/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F710476795704610%2Fposts%2F3976973512388239%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=Jsj5S9oV5Ro3bsckYFcJfPsUKqL2I5G2E%2FT5UXudKlU%3D&h=445e36d7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/710476795704610/posts/3976973512388239/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"129839a7048923c26b4ce963b10b9e2f074837a2","tid":2445343,"uid":366932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:22:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0e7dcb250c889df1c5b6b697c8e40070919ee69","tid":2445343,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:22:21.000Z","msg":"⋯"},{"pid":"ef892761d8f953418adbdbc8932eeba069d2e0d9","tid":2445343,"uid":126325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66c7f97e93c348a1899c7314838f9da5e3327aef","tid":2445343,"uid":77973,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:23:43.000Z","msg":"入面養隻狗都食牛扒啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43e2ca52519dff0ca254d49aa89c3026e10b27db","tid":2445343,"uid":300006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:23:44.000Z","msg":"無準備和牛"},{"pid":"eed31a2dd10e875f82cbfe5136faf12c5af9a02a","tid":2445343,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:23:55.000Z","msg":"山竹好,天鴿又好,2012又好,927又好,UFO又好,有咩事發生都唔驚,,要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然,,到有日真係出現 全香港範圍MAP炮 就咩都唔使<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米,[現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右]米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿,到中國午餐肉,回煱肉,,豆,菜,金寶湯<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一箱箱未開太多,,放到出廳[依d全部係魚]<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n水污染,未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐,現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食面 有 5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n另外,,打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支,,<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n來吧~~~<br />\n大混亂~~~<br />\n特大災難~~~<br />\n無水~~無電~~無野買的日子呀~~~<br />\n<br />\n期待,手持午餐肉就可以有西屌的日子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7ce114a9f996d8bc27bd0b8017636183b5af617","tid":2445343,"uid":58841,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:25:31.000Z","msg":"真係派午餐肉<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4061f8650c786b12280d766f29b6cd524b65e485","tid":2445343,"uid":129138,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T14:27:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62bc7f545d553b9cfeb50e2a95a2ae06eec52a83","tid":2445343,"uid":20625,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T15:07:01.000Z","msg":"羅便臣道都敢封<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e122b141c746324e5c9859cf3fefc011e5f2c4e9","tid":2445343,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T15:09:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/